    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔎 RAG Retriever (sub-workflow / agent tool)\n**query → embed (Ollama `nomic-embed-text`) → Qdrant search `cp_docs` → top-4 snippets + sources.**\n\nCalled by the *CP Docs RAG Agent* as the `search_cp_docs` tool. To test it alone: pin `{ \"query\": \"How do I enable Identity Awareness?\" }` on the trigger and Execute.\n\nRun the `rag-ingest` job first so `cp_docs` has vectors.",
